 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"唔想煩嘅直接租張ETC Card就得<br />\n非繁忙時間過通常自動有折扣，最後計埋唔會貴過買pass好多，甚至平過用pass"},{"pid":"59934824e84047a8be510366c272a08fa5d7945f","tid":1729261,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:39:22.000Z","msg":"認真回你, budget 呢間租車行可以唔洗買晒咁多日既KEP. 但需要連續日數， 唔係以指定DAY 1, DAY2 , DAY4 咁買, 一定要3日連住去。<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 希望香港人可以放鬆一下, 沖一沖電再係香港幫手。"},{"pid":"b4c8e7ae5554304776bd105ef0be96e26e875975","tid":1729261,"uid":32759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"搭單問北海道公路pass<br />\n如果會去函館 登別 札幌 旭川 紋別 十勝川 層雲峽<br />\n係咪基本上買pass一定有賺<br />\n佢有d highway好似唔包但唔識邊條打邊條"},{"pid":"8c63e19d61754613fabe6fe2c50edf82773e0b18","tid":1729261,"uid":265462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"用pass要在公路收費亭停底開閘 但唔洗比錢<br />\n日本收費站唔係autotoll 唔可以飛車<br />\n舊pass 係獨立放在右下位置 可隨時取走唔用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d5da4b55817d53e83d8c904c19c39c0d22ff79","tid":1729261,"uid":136952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"你去邊？<br />\n我之前又係租3日車福岡去阿蘇黑川由布別府再返福岡<br />\nKep 3日pass，都係平左600yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔買都無所謂，直接etc就得"},{"pid":"28dc715a95b69172b4c7aa9f6d29467b96fee6af","tid":1729261,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c63e19d61754613fabe6fe2c50edf82773e0b18","tid":1729261,"uid":265462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"用pass要在公路收費亭停底開閘 但唔洗比錢<br />\n日本收費站唔係autotoll 唔可以飛車<br />\n舊pass 係獨立放在右下位置 可隨時取走唔用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"點解之前係北海道係直過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37c371bb4c34ad5f33c2f5d2efca215ca187cb3","tid":1729261,"uid":265462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28dc715a95b69172b4c7aa9f6d29467b96fee6af","tid":1729261,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c63e19d61754613fabe6fe2c50edf82773e0b18","tid":1729261,"uid":265462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"用pass要在公路收費亭停底開閘 但唔洗比錢<br />\n日本收費站唔係autotoll 唔可以飛車<br />\n舊pass 係獨立放在右下位置 可隨時取走唔用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"點解之前係北海道係直過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"我都係開北海道 直過？"},{"pid":"74c6c5cfc56aaf81379704a1e98d276ed2f3e42c","tid":1729261,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傳說中的兔子天堂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家有沒有去過<span style=\"color: gold;\">日本「兔仔島」</span>大久野島？這裡有幾千隻自由自在的兔子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjLnNOtD_sOk&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=9f40f9e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyAoXHKDcW8I&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=9960d1ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I</a><br />\n<br />\n但其實島內, 不是每隻兔子都活得開心和長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predator)威脅，但很多有病, 沒有足夠糧食和營養, 所以兔迷下次去最好帶乾草(Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等)和蔬菜🥬。給牠們最基本的高纖維糧食。不要給高糖份和零食, 例如：蘿蔔、水果。<br />\n<br />\n當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=f12fd2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a><br />\n<br />\n憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=cdf35cc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a><br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。<br />\n<br />\n兔子因生病(痙攣)而憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=779904a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊來源:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=de7898e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me</a>"},{"pid":"419684b161f08e342f6702feddbef919dbf843a8","tid":1729261,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c8e7ae5554304776bd105ef0be96e26e875975","tid":1729261,"uid":32759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"搭單問北海道公路pass<br />\n如果會去函館 登別 札幌 旭川 紋別 十勝川 層雲峽<br />\n係咪基本上買pass一定有賺<br />\n佢有d highway好似唔包但唔識邊條打邊條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"北海道pass一定賺緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}